description:
Create your own wedding bands with the help of Master Goldsmith Dino Giannetti over the course of a Saturday afternoon.

Private wedding band classes cost $350 plus HST and does not include the cost of materials (white or yellow gold).

Class includes a one-hour consultation with Dino to discuss the style and materials (type and karat of gold) to be used during the workshop as well as the materials costs. 

Workshops must be booked 4 weeks in advance and are typically run on Saturdays. Please contact 18Karat to schedule the day of the workshop.

THIS DEPOSIT IS REQUIRED TO FOR INITIAL BOOKING OF THE CLASS AND DOES NOT CONSTITUTE FULL PAYMENT FOR THE CLASS - THE BALANCE OWING FOR THE CLASS AND MATERIALS IS DUE BEFORE THE CLASS BEGINS ON ITS SCHEDULED DAY.

For more information on our Wedding Band Workshop - please visit www.18karat.ca/workshops.html or call us at 416.593.1648.

name: BRIDAL JEWELLERY PARTY - $150 DEPOSIT
description:
A uniquely creative bridal party - create your bridal jewellery collection to be worn on the big day and keepsakes to treasure for a lifetime.

Whether it is pearls, crystals, or coloured gemstones 18Karat offers customizable packages to ensure a bridal collection perfectly tailored to your style.

Bridal Jewellery Party classes runs on Saturday afternoons from 12pm - 4pm and require a minimum attendance of 3 people.

Bridal Jewellery Party classes begin at $150 plus HST per person and includes all materials.

Bookings are required a minimum of 3 weeks in advance.

THIS DEPOSIT IS REQUIRED TO FOR INITIAL BOOKING OF THE CLASS AND DOES NOT CONSTITUTE FULL PAYMENT FOR THE CLASS - THE BALANCE OWING FOR THE CLASS IS DUE BEFORE THE CLASS BEGINS ON ITS SCHEDULED DAY.
